## Summary
This documentation explains the Pathfinder chart in Amplitude, which visualizes user flows through a product by displaying event sequences (paths) users take toward conversion. The chart shows both incoming and outgoing paths for specified events, with features including session-based tracking, event filtering, segmentation options, and visualization through Sankey and funnel diagrams.

